'''Cinemateca Argentina''' is a [[film archive]] located in [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]]. It was established in 1949.<ref>[http://www.cinematecaargentina.org.ar/index.php/quienes-somos Institucional] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029070419/http://www.cinematecaargentina.org.ar/index.php/quienes-somos |date=2015-10-29 }}</ref> It holds more than 22,000 films, 80,000 photographs and a library.
