==Editor==

[[File:Front cover of Musa Piscatrix.jpg|thumb|upright|''Musa Piscatrix'', first UK edition, 1896]]
[[File:The Long Road to Victory.jpg|thumb|upright|''The Long Road to Victory'', first UK edition, 1920]]

Buchan was the general editor of the ''Teaching of History'' series, published by [[Thomas Nelson (publisher)|T. Nelson Publishers]] between 1928 and 1930. In 1900 he was also a member of the editorial board of ''[[The Spectator]]''.<ref name="Gage CA" />

